entries.title: React Native Free Lancer
entries.description: Began my career as a freelance React Native developer, delivering high-quality mobile applications for diverse clients. Focused on building intuitive and performance-optimized apps for both iOS and Android platforms. Successfully completed projects ranging from healthcare and wellness solutions to e-commerce and real-time communication apps. Developed expertise in state management, third-party integrations, and creating seamless user experiences, while continuously improving my skills in mobile app development.

entries.title: Full Stack MERN and React native developer
entries.description: During my tenure at Wise360, I worked extensively as a Full Stack MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js) and React Native Developer. My role involved building and optimizing scalable web and mobile applications, implementing robust backend services, and delivering seamless user experiences.
